msgid "WooCommerce"
msgstr "WooCommerce"

#. translators: %s: link to the WooCommerce plugin on wordpress.org (anchor text "WooCommerce").
#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:75
#, php-format
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce requires the WooCommerce plugin to be installed and active. You can download %s here. If you want this plugin developed for your eCommerce platform, please send us a message."
msgstr "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce necesita que el plugin WooCommerce esté instalado y activo. Puedes descargar %s aquí. Si quieres que este plugin se desarrolle para tu plataforma de comercio electrónico, por favor, envíanos un mensaje."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:95
msgid "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce requires your website to have a valid HTTPS/SSL certificate."
msgstr "Product Recommendation Quiz for eCommerce necesita que tu web tenga un certificado HTTPS/SSL válido."

#: admin/class-product-recommendation-quiz-for-ecommerce-admin-diagnostics.php:109
msgid "This plugin does not work on local environments. It needs to be installed on a live website. Your website needs to be public and not hidden by a site under construction plugin because it needs connection to our server in order to work."
msgstr "Este plugin no funciona en entornos locales. Tiene que ser instalado en una web en producción. Tu web debe ser pública y no estar oculta por un plugin de «sitio en construcción» porque necesita conexión a nuestro servidor para poder funcionar."

